snippet.title: Harry Potter: Quidditch Champions - Official Trailer - "Welcome Students!"
snippet.description:
ATTENTION future Quidditch stars, it's time to approach the pitch! Grab your broom, pick your position, and prepare to take flight.
Harry Potter: Quidditch Champions is available digitally September 3.

Pre-order the Standard or Deluxe Edition now on Xbox, Steam, & Epic Games Store to earn the Firebolt Supreme broom skin. For
PlayStation Plus* members, the Standard edition of #QuidditchChampions and the Firebolt Supreme boom skin will be available
from September 3 – 30th, 2024.

https://www.quidditchchampions.com/purchase

*Monthly games accessible for duration of PS Plus membership only. PS Plus is an ongoing subscription with recurring fees until
cancelled. Age restrictions apply. Full terms: play.st/psplus-usageterms

#QuidditchChampions #HarryPotter #WizardingWorld
